HEADWORD: Spoilsmonger
<hw>Spoils"mon`ger</hw> <pr>(spoilz"m⟦ucr⟧⟦nsm⟧`g⟦etil⟧r)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <def>One who promises or distributes public offices and
